The paper presents a new approach for panoptic segmentation, which is a task related to computer vision and image analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new model architecture, which could be relevant to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
